/div></div><div class="margin"><div class="twelve columns"><h3>Accessing your Camera´s SD Card</h3></div></div><div class="card-container margin"><div class="onecard twelve columns"><amp-youtube data-videoid="PESNN3KxKNU" layout="responsive" width="480" height="270" class="shadow"></amp-youtube></div></div><div class="card-container margin"><div class="onecard twelve columns"><amp-youtube data-videoid="CG0h7wD0spM" layout="responsive" width="480" height="270" class="shadow"></amp-youtube></div></div><div class="margin"><div class="twelve columns margin"><h1>Alternative IP Scanner</h1></div></div><div class="card-container margin"><div class="twocard"><div class="image"><amp-img class="shadow" noloading height=190 width=297 layout=responsive src="/images/angryIP.jpg"></amp-img> <span class="title">Angry IP Scanner</span></div><div class="content"><p>Angry IP scanner is a very fast open-source IP address and port scanner. It is available for Windows, MacOSX as well as Linux.</p></div><div class="action"> <a href="/Quick_Installation/Alternative_IP_Scanner/Angry_IP_Scanner">Read More</a></div></div><div class="twocard"><div class="image"><amp-img class="shadow" noloading height=190 width=297 layout=responsive src="/images/fingCLI.jpg"></amp-img> <span class="title">Fing CLI</span></div><div class="content"><p>Fing is an easy-to-use command line tool to keep an eye on your local IP network. The software is available for Windows, macOS and LINUX.</p></div><div class="action"> <a href="/Quick_Installation/Alternative_IP_Scanner/Fing_CLI">Read More</a></div></div></div><div class="card-container"><div class="twocard"><div class="image"><amp-img class="shadow" noloading height=190 width=297 layout=responsive src="/images/fingAndroid.jpg"></amp-img> <span class="title">Fing Mobile</span></div><div class="content"><p>Easily discover all the devices on your personal and professional networks from your mobile phone. Available for Android and iOS.</p></div><div class="action"> <